{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":107,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我想了很久，却还是想不出牒儿布和布达拉天王会是什么人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":16,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"既然想不出，又何必去想？","tone":"轻笑","chapter":21,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我不能不想。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"人们为什么总是要去想一些他本不该想的事。","tone":"无奈","chapter":21,"line_start":24,"line_end":26},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我想，牒儿布天王一定是个很有智谋的人，布达拉天王一定很孤高骄傲。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"魔教中取的名字，当然绝不会是没有道理的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":34,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"以你看，现在长安城里最有智慧的人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是你！","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只有智者，才有慧剑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"大智若愚，真正的聪明人，看起来也许像个呆子。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":21,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"长安城里，看来像呆子的人倒不少，真正的呆子也不少。","tone":"轻笑","chapter":21,"line_start":48,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"你认为最孤高骄傲的人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"你！","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"又是我。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":21,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"只有最骄傲的人，才会拒绝别人的真情好意。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"除了你之外，也许还有一两个人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":68,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"吕迪、郭定。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"他们当然都绝不是魔教中的人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"是不是因为他们的出身好，家世好，所以就不会入魔教？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":76,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"我只不过觉得他们都没有魔教门下的那种邪气。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"不管怎么样，牒儿布和布达拉都已在长安城，也许就是你最想不到的两个人，因为他们的行踪一向都是别人永远想不到的，这才真正是魔教最邪的地方。","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"只要他们的确已到了长安城，我迟早总会找到他们的。","tone":"得意","chapter":21,"line_start":94,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"可是今天你还不能开始找。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_ye_kai","speaker_name":"叶开","listener":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":100,"line_end":100},{"speaker":"char_shang_guan_xiao_xian","speaker_name":"上官小仙","listener":"char_ye_kai","text":"因为，今天你一定要先到鸿宾客栈去喝喜酒。因为你若不去，有很多人都会伤心的。","tone":"调侃","chapter":21,"line_start":102,"line_end":104}],"new_entities":{},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":108,"line_end":196,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"这人参是不是很贵？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":128,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我们能买得起？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"买不起。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"那么你是……","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"是我赊来的，因为我想今天一定有很多人会送礼来，长安城里，一定有很多人想来看我们，喝两杯我们的喜酒，这些人一定都不会是很小气的人。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":140,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我们的事，已经有很多人知道？","tone":"犹豫","chapter":21,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"所以我已叫掌柜的替我们准备了十二桌喜酒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":146,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_guo_ding","speaker_name":"郭定","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"其实你本不必这么做的，我……","tone":"激动","chapter":21,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_guo_ding","text":"你只要打起精神来，赶快把伤养好，千万不要让我做寡妇。","tone":"柔声","chapter":21,"line_start":152,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"丁姑娘你已该出来打扮打扮了，我也已找人来替郭公子洗澡换衣裳。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":164,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"你真是个好人。","tone":"温柔","chapter":21,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"今天是大年初一，我只盼望今年大家都过得顺遂，大家都开心。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":174,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"现在是不是已经有人送了礼来。","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":184,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"送礼的人可真不少，我已把送来的礼都记了账，丁姑娘是不是想去看看。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":188,"line_end":190}],"new_entities":{},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":197,"line_end":277,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"你看过这人送来的字画没有？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":254,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"丁姑娘若是想看看，我现在就可以去拿出来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":256,"line_end":258}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_yang_tian","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":196,"line_end":200,"text":"飞狐杨天送礼：珠花一对，碧玉镯一双，赤金头面全套，纯金古钱四十枚，共重四百两"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":278,"line_end":353,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"这里是不是鸿宾客栈？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":278,"line_end":279},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"小号正是鸿宾。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":286,"line_end":286},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"郭定郭公子和丁灵琳丁姑娘的喜事，是不是就在这里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":288,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"正是在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":292,"line_end":292},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"客官是来找郭公子的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":296,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"不是。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"是来送礼的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":302,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"也不是。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"不送礼也一样可以喝喜酒，四位就请后面坐，先请用茶。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":306,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"我们不喝茶，也不是来喝喜酒的。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":310,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"那么你们莫非想来看新娘子？","tone":"调侃","chapter":21,"line_start":312,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你就是新娘子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":314,"line_end":314},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"所以你们假如要看，现在就可以看了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":316,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我们要来看的并不是新娘子。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":318,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"你们来看什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":320,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"来看今天晚上有没有敢到这里来惹事生非的人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":322,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"假如有呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":324,"line_end":324},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"不能有，也不会有。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":326,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"为什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"因为我们已奉命来保护这里的安全，保护新人平平安安的进洞房。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":330,"line_end":332},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"有你们在这里，就不会再有人来惹事生非？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":334,"line_end":334},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"若是有一个人敢来，长安城里今夜就要多一个死人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":336,"line_end":336},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"若有一百个人敢来，长安城里就要多一百个死人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":338,"line_end":338},{"speaker":"char_huang_yi_ren","speaker_name":"黄衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"多一百另四个。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":340,"line_end":340},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"你们是奉了谁的命令而来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":344,"line_end":344},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_huang_yi_ren","text":"你们是不是金钱帮的人？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":348,"line_end":348}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_huang_yi_ren","name":"黄衣人","alias":["黄袍黑发中年人"],"identity":"身份不明的神秘护卫","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":null,"one_line":"四个黄袍黑发的神秘人，奉命保护鸿宾客栈婚礼安全","personality":{"traits":["冷酷","沉默","忠诚","坚定","神秘"],"speech_style":"冷淡简短","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":282,"line_end":284,"text":"问话的是个黄袍黑发的中年人，身上的长袍盖膝，黄得发亮"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":5,"line_start":354,"line_end":414,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"你来得太早了，现在还没有到发赏的时候。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":362,"line_end":364},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"你怎么知道我是来讨赏的？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":366,"line_end":366},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"你不是？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":368,"line_end":368},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"你就算把这客栈送给我，我也未必会要。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":370,"line_end":370},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"难道你也是来喝喜酒的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":374,"line_end":374},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"不是。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":376,"line_end":376},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"你来干什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":378,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"来送礼。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"礼物在哪里？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":384,"line_end":384},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"就在这里。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":386,"line_end":386},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"这些都是送给丁姑娘添妆的，你好生收下。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":400,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_qi_gai","text":"大爷高姓？","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":402,"line_end":402},{"speaker":"char_qi_gai","speaker_name":"乞丐","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"我不是大爷，我是个穷要饭的。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":404,"line_end":404}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_qi_gai","name":"乞丐","alias":["鹑衣百结的乞丐","披头散发的乞丐"],"identity":"身份不明的神秘人物，身法极快，送大量珠宝给丁灵琳","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":null,"one_line":"鹑衣百结、身法如陀螺的神秘乞丐，送奇珍异宝为丁灵琳添妆","personality":{"traits":["古怪","冷傲","神秘","豪爽","不羁"],"speech_style":"冷硬简洁","temperament":"孤傲"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":358,"line_end":360,"text":"来的竟是个鹑衣百结，披头散发的乞丐，还背着口破破烂烂的大麻袋"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_mo_jiao_yu_pai","name":"魔教玉牌","type":"special","owner":"char_qi_gai","one_line":"乞丐送来的珠宝中附带的刻有四个魔神的玉牌","description":"一块玉牌，上面刻着四个魔神，一个手执智磐，一个手执法杖，一个手托山峰，还有一个手里竟托着赤裸的女人。此物与魔教有关。","effects":["身份标识","魔教信物"],"origin":"魔教","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_qi_gai"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":606,"line_end":608,"text":"上面刻着的，是四个魔神，一个手执智磐，一个手执法杖，一个手托山峰，还有一个手里竟托着赤裸的女人"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":6,"line_start":415,"line_end":575,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"丁姑娘也不认得他们四位？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":418,"line_end":418},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"非但不认得，连这四个名字都没听过。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":21,"line_start":420,"line_end":420},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"姑娘若连他们的名字都未听过，他们怎么会送如此重的礼？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":424,"line_end":426},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"不管怎么样，人家送礼来，总是好意。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":430,"line_end":430},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"这里是不是有个姓郭的在办喜事？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":444,"line_end":446},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"客官是来送礼的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":448,"line_end":450},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"不是。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":452,"line_end":452},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"是来喝喜酒的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":454,"line_end":454},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_lao_zhang_gui","text":"也不是。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":456,"line_end":456},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你就是南宫浪？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":460,"line_end":460},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"南宫浪算什么东西。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":462,"line_end":462},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"他的确不是个东西。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":464,"line_end":464},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我是东西。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":466,"line_end":466},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你为什么不问，我是什么东西？","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":470,"line_end":470},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我正想问。","tone":"好奇","chapter":21,"line_start":472,"line_end":472},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我是礼物。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":474,"line_end":474},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你姓李？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":476,"line_end":476},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"不是姓李的李，是礼物。","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":478,"line_end":478},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你就是丁灵琳？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":484,"line_end":484},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"今天就是你大喜的日子？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":488,"line_end":488},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"所以有人送我来做贺礼，你懂不懂？","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":492,"line_end":492},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你是说，有人把你当做礼物送给我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":494,"line_end":496},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你总算懂了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":21,"line_start":498,"line_end":498},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我不懂。","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":500,"line_end":500},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"还不懂？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":502,"line_end":502},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我要你这么样一个礼物干什么？","tone":"苦笑","chapter":21,"line_start":504,"line_end":504},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"当然有用。","tone":"得意","chapter":21,"line_start":506,"line_end":506},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"有什么用？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":508,"line_end":508},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我能救人的命。","tone":"得意","chapter":21,"line_start":510,"line_end":510},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"救谁的命？","tone":"焦急","chapter":21,"line_start":512,"line_end":512},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"救你老公郭定。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":514,"line_end":514},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你能救得了他？","tone":"激动","chapter":21,"line_start":516,"line_end":516},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我若救不了他，天下就绝没有第二个人还能救得了他。","tone":"得意","chapter":21,"line_start":518,"line_end":520},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我不是来给你看的，也不喜欢女人盯着我看。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":526,"line_end":526},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我知道。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":528,"line_end":528},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你知道？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":530,"line_end":530},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我也知道你是什么人了。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":21,"line_start":532,"line_end":532},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"蓝衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":534,"line_end":534},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你姓葛，你就是'万宝箱，乾坤伞，阎王没法管'的葛病。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":21,"line_start":536,"line_end":538},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你见过葛病？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":540,"line_end":540},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我没有见过，可是我听叶开谈起过。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":542,"line_end":542},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":544,"line_end":544},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"他说葛病从小就多病，而且没有人能治得了他的病，所以他就想法子自己治，到后来竟成了天下第一神医，连阎王都管不了他，因为死人也常常被他救活。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":546,"line_end":548},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"叶开又算是什么东西？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":550,"line_end":550},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"他不是东西，他是你的朋友，我知道……","tone":"激动","chapter":21,"line_start":552,"line_end":552},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"是不是叶开叫你来的，他是不是还没有死？","tone":"激动","chapter":21,"line_start":554,"line_end":556},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你找错人了。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":558,"line_end":558},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"我没有。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":560,"line_end":560},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你是新娘子，你应该去找你的老公，为什么拉住我？","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":562,"line_end":562},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"也许我真的找错人了。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":21,"line_start":568,"line_end":570},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"但我却没有找错。","tone":"认真","chapter":21,"line_start":572,"line_end":572},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你……你要找郭定？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":574,"line_end":574},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你若不想做寡妇，就赶快带我去。","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":576,"line_end":576}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ge_bing","name":"葛病","alias":["蓝衣人","万宝箱乾坤伞阎王没法管"],"identity":"天下第一神医，身患怪病却自医成才","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":null,"one_line":"身着蓝衫、手持乾坤伞和万宝箱的天下第一神医，号称连阎王都管不了他","personality":{"traits":["古怪","孤傲","自信","冷淡","深藏不露","医术超群"],"speech_style":"冷淡简洁","temperament":"孤高"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":440,"line_end":442,"text":"这个人身上居然只穿着件蓝衫，头上却戴顶形式奇古的高帽，蜡黄的脸，稀稀疏疏的山羊胡子"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":7,"line_start":576,"line_end":660,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"这是谁送来的？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":582,"line_end":584},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"是个乞丐。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":586,"line_end":586},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"什么样的乞丐？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":588,"line_end":588},{"speaker":"char_lao_zhang_gui","speaker_name":"老掌柜","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"是个年纪不太大的乞丐，总是喜欢翻白眼，说起话来，总像是要找人吵架。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":592,"line_end":594},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"他的身法很快，而且很奇怪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":596,"line_end":596},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"哪点奇怪？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":598,"line_end":598},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"他身子打转的时候，就像是个陀螺一样。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":600,"line_end":600},{"speaker":"char_ge_bing","speaker_name":"葛病","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"这些珠宝里，是不是有块上面刻着四个妖魔的玉牌。","tone":"严肃","chapter":21,"line_start":602,"line_end":604},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"你知道这四个人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":612,"line_end":612},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_ge_bing","text":"南宫浪，我就知道你会来的。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":678,"line_end":678},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我不是南宫浪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":680,"line_end":680},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"你不是？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":682,"line_end":682},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"我是来送礼的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":684,"line_end":684},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"为什么直到现在才来送礼？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":686,"line_end":686},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"虽然送得迟了些，总比不送好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":688,"line_end":688},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"这就是你送来的礼？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":690,"line_end":690}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_nan_gong_lang","name":"南宫浪","alias":["黑衣人"],"identity":"南宫世家最可怕的人，声名狼藉的大盗，南宫远的嫡亲叔叔","faction":"南宫世家","role":"villain","archetype":"assassin","rank":null,"one_line":"南宫世家最凶狠恶毒的不肖子弟，声名狼藉的大盗，前来刺杀郭定","personality":{"traits":["凶狠","恶毒","狡猾","残忍","阴险"],"speech_style":"阴冷简洁","temperament":"暴戾"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_nan_gong_yuan","type":"亲属","intensity":50,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"叔侄"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[21],"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":248,"line_end":252,"text":"南宫浪就是南宫世家中最可怕的人。他是个声名狼藉的大盗，是南宫世家的不肖子弟，但他却也是南宫远的嫡亲叔叔"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":8,"line_start":661,"line_end":772,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"你若认为我送的礼有恶意，你就错了。","tone":"淡然","chapter":21,"line_start":702,"line_end":702},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"这难道还是好意？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":21,"line_start":704,"line_end":704},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"非但是好意，而且我可以保证，今天来的客人里，绝没有任何人送的礼比我这份礼更贵重。","tone":"得意","chapter":21,"line_start":706,"line_end":708},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"哦？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":710,"line_end":710},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"因为这个人若是不死，两位今天只怕就很难平平安安的过你们的洞房花烛夜。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":712,"line_end":714},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"这个人是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":716,"line_end":716},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"是个一心要来取你们项上人头的人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":21,"line_start":718,"line_end":718},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"是南宫浪？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":21,"line_start":720,"line_end":720},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"不错，就是他。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":722,"line_end":722},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"你是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":724,"line_end":724},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"本来也是南宫浪的仇人。","tone":"陈述","chapter":21,"line_start":726,"line_end":726},{"speaker":"char_ding_lin_lin","speaker_name":"丁灵琳","listener":"char_nan_gong_lang","text":"现在呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":21,"line_start":728,"line_end":728},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":"char_ding_lin_lin","text":"现在是个已送过了礼，正等着要喝喜酒的客人。","tone":"微笑","chapter":21,"line_start":730,"line_end":730},{"speaker":"char_nan_gong_lang","speaker_name":"黑衣人","listener":null,"text":"什么人？","tone":"厉声","chapter":21,"line_start":738,"line_end":738}],"new_entities":{},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_nan_gong_lang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":21,"line_start":672,"line_end":674,"text":"一个黑衣佩剑，脸色惨白，就像是幽灵般突然出现的人"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
